{"tid":1557158,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】消息：警新購一萬支伸縮警棍　專供休班警跟身執法","createTime":"2019-09-10T04:08:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T04:23:47.000Z","uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4deea84c47fbe69d532b767fb1f2f37e3589eae1","tid":1557158,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:08:21.000Z","msg":"修例風波未平息，衍生的警民衝突加劇。據了解，警隊內部已傳開消息，支援科早前新購入約萬支伸縮警棍，專為警務人員休班時隨身攜帶。《香港01》今日（10日）獲得一份警方支援科發出、名為《發放伸縮警棍予休班警》的文件，指為配合近月的「踏浪者行動」需要，助理警務處長（支援）已批准向警務人員額外派發伸縮警棍，「以期讓人員於休班期間執行警察職務」。最快會於今日下午發放。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》正待警方回覆。<br />\n<br />\n可以周圍扑人頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c09bd22a59eb11604bef2c3955e31b3f8e4fe4f9","tid":1557158,"uid":46148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:10:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">點解買警棍可以有成幾個post 重要一齊狂推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"672948e4e446a6b292c5b44bdf3727babbb77502","tid":1557158,"uid":242537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T04:23:47.000Z","msg":"支畜01 果然係香港 既垃圾新畜黨喉舌<br />\n請大家快速del撚咗去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EEEp8plU4AAf1WF?format=jpg&amp;name=medium\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FEEEp8plU4AAf1WF%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dmedium&h=4a44f028&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 <br />\n咁咪可以隨時隨地都可以仆頭 打撚死普通香港市民<br />\n屌你<br />\n仆街狗屎垃圾比膠超 含撚蔥"}]}